data.description: 6.5% 7/1 ARM financing available for qualified buyers under contract by December 31, 2023. This beautiful & spacious, nicely updated Forrester boasts an open floor plan & features: A vaulted & beamed, sun-filled, formal living room & spacious formal dining room that's perfect for family dinners; Kitchen with newer stainless steel appliances; Breakfast area with door to the concrete patio overlooking the fenced yard; Family room with cozy stone fireplace; Double door access to the master suite that offers a walk-in closet & private bath; Updated bath#2 with gray marble vanity; Bedrooms 2&3 with ample closet space; Partially finished, English, look-out basement. Gleaming plank laminate flooring throughout most of the home. Newer AC & Furnace (11 years), Water heater (1 year), Roof (12 years).
